The paper presents a deep learning technique-based method to solve large-scale 0-1 knapsack problems, which is a fundamental problem in computer science, business, and operations research. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), robotics (cs.RO), and computer vision (cs.CV).
